{"tid":2320375,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"達明《今天世上所有地方》iTunes壓倒Eason登榜首　 黃耀明繼續唱「自由必將釋放」","createTime":"2020-12-10T18:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T04:30:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0730b460412b9c2d73c9d6b181e60e1cb49736","tid":2320375,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T18:38:26.000Z","msg":"達明一派成員黃耀明勇於發聲，達明之前為演唱會找來潘源良為新歌《今天世上所有地方》填詞，延續1988年金曲《今天應該很高興》，昨日新歌贏了陳奕迅（Eason）的《是但求其愛》和謝安琪《三生一吻》等，登上iTunes香港地區排行榜第一位。黃耀明昨日接受《蘋果》訪問，對於成績好感到相當開心，不過他也引用新歌歌詞「要相信自由必將釋放」，指在世上任何一個地方，也可以為香港做很多事。<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明及劉以達組成的達明一派，上月中在伊館舉行六場演唱會，除重新演繹「六四」前後兩張唱片《意難平》及《神經》外，在encore時更率先演唱新歌《今天世上所有地方》，並將歌曲獻給在世界各地的朋友、手足及同路人。<a href=\"http://新歌於上周日已先在何韻詩網店hall1c.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8C%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E5%B7%B2%E5%85%88%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E7%B6%B2%E5%BA%97hall1c.com&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqRFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=eba3dcb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">新歌於上周日已先在何韻詩網店hall1c.com</a>上架，到上周二在iTunes香港地區上架，昨日更衝上iTunes香港地區熱門歌曲第一位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/WIJL5B4CTFAKNC7NFBOMRHX7GQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FWIJL5B4CTFAKNC7NFBOMRHX7GQ%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqRFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=ca0124ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FWIJL5B4CTFAKNC7NFBOMRHX7GQ%2F&h=f47f92f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/WIJL5B4CTFAKNC7NFBOMRHX7GQ/</a>"},{"pid":"d8ebff233ddc0b7be72377ec09ba3bc5a52e8431","tid":2320375,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T18:51:09.000Z","msg":"唔講政治，三生一吻好撚好聽"},{"pid":"897978ba85a59b49fdd51b5d83b5663c528ae0ce","tid":2320375,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-1